FIG. 2 is a circuit diagram showing an apparatus for controlling a cooling unit in which DC motors are used to enhance energy efficiency;


FIG. 3 is a circuit diagram showing an apparatus for controlling a cooling unit in a preferred embodiment according to the invention; and


FIG. 4 is a timing chart shoving operation of the apparatus for controlling a cooling unit in the preferred embodiment in the invention.
